immer im Fishy Fingers.

692
00:54:22,400 --> 00:54:24,000
Im Fishy Fingers?

693
00:54:24,000 --> 00:54:26,800
Diesem verruchten Gasthaus an der Themse?

694
00:54:26,800 --> 00:54:31,200
